    "Our review topic and domain lent themselves well to the socio-technical research context supported by socio-technical grounded theory (STGT) where our domain was AI, the actors were AI practitioners, the researcher team was collectively well versed in qualitative research and the AI domain, and the data was collected from relevant sources (Hoda 2021)."
